        "sendTo": "vdakpogan@onpointafrica.com, ekouassi@onpointafrica.com, mngbra@onpointafrica.com, agnaore@onpointafrica.com",
        "subject": "=⚠️ KB Emma — {{ $json.nbNonTraites }} question(s) non traitée(s) en attente",
        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;background:#f1f5f9;padding:24px 12px;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);padding:24px 28px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#94a3b8;\">Assistant IA — Suivi KB</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin:0;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#f8fafc;\">Backlog à documenter</h1>\n</div>\n<div style=\"padding:24px 28px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff7ed;border:1px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#c2410c;\">{{ $json.nbNonTraites }}</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#9a3412;font-weight:600;\">question(s) sans réponse KB — non traitée(s)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#b45309;\">Seuil configuré : {{ $json.seuil }} · Total logs : {{ $json.nbTotal }}</p>\n</div>\n{{ $json.apercu.length > 0 ? '<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">Aperçu des plus récentes</p><ul style=\"margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none;\">' + $json.apercu.map(q => '<li style=\"margin:0 0 8px;padding:10px 14px 10px 14px;background:#fffbeb;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;font-size:13px;color:#422006;\">' + q + '</li>').join('') + '</ul>' : '' }}\n<hr style=\"margin:20px 0;border:0;border-top:1px solid #f1f5f9;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\">➡️ Ouvrir la Data Table <strong>logs chatbot support</strong> dans n8n, enrichir la KB et passer <strong>traite = oui</strong> une fois fait.<br>Le prochain rapport hebdo reflétera les changements.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
